{"word":"μελάνω","slug":"μελάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n65930\" key=\"mela/nw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μελάν-ω</orth>, intr., <sense id=\"n65930.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">grow black</tr_>, only in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:64\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.64</biblScope> </bibl> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ζεφύροιο ἐχεύατο πόντον ἔπι φρίξ . . , μελάνει δέ τε πόντος ὑπ᾽ αὐτῆς</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῆς φρικός</foreign>), cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg036:934a:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">934a15</biblScope> </bibl>; but <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author> </bibl> read <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πόντον</foreign> in the second clause and took <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μελάνει</foreign> trans., <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">μελαίνει</ref> </xr> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ζέφυρος</foreign>), <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">makes</tr_> the sea <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">black</tr_>:—later writers use <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μελανέω</orth>, intr. (which implies the reading <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μελανεῖ δέ τε πόντος</foreign>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg005:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ign.\">Ign.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">50</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:1574\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.1574</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:836\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">836</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ καλὸν μελανεῦντα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0533.tlg003.perseus-grc1:53\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Epigr.\">Epigr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">53</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μικκὴ καὶ μελανεῦσα</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.120</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phld.\">Phld.</a></author> </bibl>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}